OL,3,CTwo men charged with murder of 'witty
OL,4,Cman with a huge heart' in Swansea
OL,6,FTwo men from Somerset have been
OL,7,Fcharged with the murder of a man who
OL,8,Fdied after spending nearly a month in
OL,9,Fhospital following an incident in
OL,10,FSwansea.
OL,12,FAndrew Main, 33, from Falkirk,
OL,13,FScotland, was involved in an incident
OL,14,Fon Princess Way, Swansea, on July 17.
OL,16,FHe died from his injuries on August 14
OL,17,Fand a murder investigation was
OL,18,Flaunched by South Wales Police.
