OL,3,CTwo men charged with murder of 'witty
OL,4,Cman with a huge heart' in Swansea
OL,6,FJoseph Dix, 26, of Frome, and Macauley
OL,7,FRuddock, 27, of Bath, both appeared at
OL,8,FSwansea Crown Court on Friday, 13
OL,9,FSeptember and pleaded not guilty.
OL,11,FIn paying tribute to her brother,
OL,12,FNikki Main described Andrew as "a
OL,13,Fwitty man with a huge heart" and urged
OL,14,Fanyone with information to come
OL,15,Fforward.
