OL,6,FShe said: "Andrew ` my baby brother `
OL,7,Fwas sadly taken from us far too soon.
OL,8,FHe was adored by family and friends
OL,9,Fand beloved by more. We are absolutely
OL,10,Fdevastated by his sudden passing and
OL,11,Fask anyone with information to please,
OL,12,Fplease come forward.
OL,14,F"He will forever live in our hearts
OL,15,Fand memories. He was a witty man with
OL,16,Fa huge heart ` loyal to the core. He
OL,17,Fwas a fabulous brother, fun uncle, and
OL,18,Fsupportive daddy to his two children.
OL,19,FThere will never be anyone like Andrew.
