OL,6,F"The hole that has been left in our
OL,7,Fhearts will never be filled. Everyone
OL,8,Fin our community has been grief-
OL,9,Fstricken, but we have rallied together
OL,10,Fas one at this sad time.
OL,12,F"As a family, we are destroyed by what
OL,13,Fhas happened to Andrew. We can't thank
OL,14,Feveryone enough for the love and
OL,15,Fsupport they have shown."
OL,17,FJoseph Dix and Macauley Ruddock are
OL,18,Fexpected to go on trial in January
OL,19,Fnext year.
